從明永曆十八（西元一六六四年）陳炳輝公來台拓荒結圧，南勢地區因地理、族群等因素，為了保莊衛民，即有崇尚習武之風並有其武力組織之必要性，自組的武力自衛組織至今應有二百年以上的歷史。而在跟隨著明清時期宋江陣傳入台灣，佳里鎮所在地蕭壠香在清朝中葉開始之後，證據顯示九龍殿宋江陣至今已有100年以上的歷史。九龍殿宋江陣歷史發展過程中，在蕭壠香中斷後，宋江陣轉而加入西港香科，並因政治因素（太平洋戰爭、二二八事件）也經過兩次中斷，此頑強的生命力生生滅滅，滅滅生生的現象，可歸納為歷史背景、地理、宗教、血緣等因素，使宋江陣中斷二次仍再恢復之生生不息之現象。在經歷歷史背景、地理、宗教、血緣等因素涵化，及經累世累代先民的傳承維護洗鍊之下，其已是相關歷史文化的載體，有完整的文化結構。其是由核心的精神思想層次主導組織、規範、制度層次之形成，並由最外層外顯物質技藝層次，表現出內層的精神思想與組織規範制度。各層次各要素間都均能直接對應相互連結，並未有從天而降無法連結與解釋前因後果之項目，因此九龍殿宋江陣的文化結構，至今已是一組織結構相當嚴密的宋江陣文化結構生態體系。此也為本研究重大發現，並應可禰補學術界至今尚未有「台灣宋江陣文化結構」相關研究之缺憾。九龍殿宋江陣文化結構各層次的內容因素為：1、精神思想層次：（1）給香科神明湊熱鬧（2）做為謝府元帥駕前部隊（3）驅邪祈求平安賜福、安定民心（4）團結鄉里（5）強身健體（6）宗族血緣凝聚（7）文化傳承與認同。2、組織、規範、制度層次：（1）組織以地域血緣為主軸，以廟方為核心發動莊民為主體所組成（2）屬黃腳巾系統同腳巾有合陣現象（3）陣法由宗教與軍事邏輯交織而成（4）入館、開館、探館、刈香、謝館（5）出陣以三年一科西港香科為週期，其他交陪境配合此週期參與。3、外顯物質技藝層次：（1）外顯器物：黃腳巾、謝籃、清淨符、紅綢、鞭炮、兵器、宋江鼓鑼鈸（2）武術拳法：有白鶴拳、飛鶴拳、羅漢拳、環花散寺、太祖拳、陳家太極拳（3）陣式：發彩、打圈、請圈、拜王爺、開二門、龍捲水、穿心、開斧、開旗、個人兵器操練、個人拳術表演、蜈蚣陣、蜘蛛結網、兵器對打、空手連環、八卦陣、七星陣。

Ever since Mr. Chen Ping-hui came to Taiwan to open up the land and formed villages in1664 (Yung-Li year 18 of Ming Dynasty), and in order to prevent the village and thevillage people at Nanshih area from being attacked due to its geographic and groupsfactors, there were customs of practicing martial customs and necessity of formingmilitary forces. The private military forces and self-defense organization have lasted morethan two hundred years. Meanwhile, along with the introduction of Sung-Chiang Paradeinto Taiwan of the Ming and Ching Dynasties, which after Hsiao-Lung Religious Serviceof Chiali Town started in the middle of Ching dynasty, it has been proved that theSung-Chiang Parade of Chiu Lung Temple has been existed more than a century.During the development of the Sung-Chiang Parade of Chiu Lung Temple, afterHsiao-Lung Religious Service stopped, the Sung-Chiang Parade was then joined toHsikang Religious Service, besides, due to the upheaval political circumstances (PacificWar, 228 Incident), the operation has been interrupted twice. There were several reasons,such as historical background, geographic, religious and blood tie, etc., made suchobstinate group, having been through ups and downs many times, of Sung-Chiang Paradesurvive and the twice interruptions and still thrive.Having been experienced and cultivated by the historical, geographic, religious and bloodtie, etc, factors, also, having been exposed and influenced by the ancestors, it has beenturned into a carrier of the related history and culture with complete cultural structure. Itis led by the core spiritual thoughts to form the organization, regulation and system, also,the inner most spiritual thought and the organization and regulation are thus displayedfrom the exposed material technique level at the outmost layer. Different levels andiiifactors among them must be able to corresponded and connected to one another, and noitems falling down from the sky cannot be connected or explained. Therefore, thecultural structure of the Sung-Chiang Parade of Chiu Lung Temple has been a wellorganized group regarding the system of Sung-Chiang Parade. This too is a significantfinding on this research, which may also make up the missing piece of the related studyon “the cultural structure of the Sung-Chiang Parade here at Taiwan” up to now.The different levels and content of the cultural structure of Sung-Chiang Parade of ChiuLung Temple are:1. Spiritual thought level:1) To join with gods of Religious Service;2) To be advance force of the Hsieh Marshal;3) To play the role as the exorcism and blessing god to give a peace of mind topeople;4) To group up the local people;5) To strengthen up the body;6) To concentrate the blood relationship of clan;7) To pass on and accept such culture.2. Organization, regulation and systematic level:1) Take the region and blood relationship as the main axis the temple as core to callup the people as main body;2) To gather the yellow foot band system group with other groups to combine for thebattle array;3) The matrix deploy shall be based on religious and military logic to form;4) To enter, open, explore, clip the incense, and perform worship ceremony on themartial art house;5) The outing of the battle array shall be held once every three year at HsikangReligious Service as a cycle, while other parade shall be based on this cycle tomake decision.iv3. The exposed material technique level:1) The exposed instrument, yellow foot band, thank-you basket, cleansing amulet,red satin, firework, arms, gong and cymbal for Sung-Chiang Parade;2) Martial art boxing includes: white crane boxing, flying crane boxing, Lohanboxing, flower spreading, Taichu boxing, Chen’s Taichi boxing;3) Matrix: Fatsai, circle, inviting, god worshiping, two-gate opening, dragon jumpout of water, through core, ax-opening, flag-opening, personal weapon practicing,personal boxing performance, centipede matrix, cobweb, weapon matching,empty-handed link circle, the 8-trigram, 7-star matrix.

